遊戲獲一致好評，評論員對圖像和戰鬥機制予以讚揚，認為與From Software的另一遊戲《[[血源詛咒|血源詛咒]]》相似<ref name="Destructoid"/><ref name="Game Informer"/><ref name="GameRev"/><ref name=IGN/><ref name="Eurogamer">{{cite web|last1=Stanton|first1=Rich|title=''Dark Souls 3'' review|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-04-04-dark-souls-3-review|website=Eurogamer|date=2016-04-04|accessdate=2016-04-05|archive-date=2016-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160405174607/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-04-04-dark-souls-3-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[IGN|IGN]]》成員Chloi Rad為遊戲給予9.5/10分，表示《黑暗靈魂III》作為《靈魂系列》的最後作品，是一款及格的送別作<ref name=IGN/>；《[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]》成員Rich Stanton以「必須要玩的」形容遊戲，指出《黑暗靈魂III》非常出色，是《靈魂系列》的合適最終作<ref name="Eurogamer"/>；《[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]》成員Steven Strom認為遊戲保留了《靈魂系列》的流暢和[[渲染|渲染]]，部分頭目戰也屬系列之冠<ref name="Ars Technica"/>；《[[衛報|衛報]]》成員Simon Parkin為遊戲給予5/5分，認為遊戲也許欠缺首作的創新，但稱得上是系列中最嶄新和完成程度最高的作品。<ref name="Guardian">{{cite web|last=Parkin|first=Simon|url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2016/apr/12/dark-souls-3-review-game-trilogy-hidetaki-miyazaki|title=''Dark Souls 3'' review – the grandiose end to an unmatched trilogy|work=The Guardian|date=2016-04-12|accessdate=2017-05-25|archive-date=2016-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160424220528/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2016/apr/12/dark-souls-3-review-game-trilogy-hidetaki-miyazaki|dead-url=no}}</ref>

遊戲的[[畫面更新率|畫面更新率]]、性能表現、直線性質的地圖設計、以及[[萬代|萬代]]對遊戲發行的處理手法備受批評<ref name="GameRev"/><ref name="Polygon"/><ref name="Ars Technica">{{cite web|last1=Strom|first1=Steven|title=''Dark Souls 3'' review: Marching toward masochism|url=http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2016/04/dark-souls-3-review-marching-towards-masochism/|website=Ars Technica|date=2016-04-05|accessdate=2016-04-05|archive-date=2016-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160406003552/http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2016/04/dark-souls-3-review-marching-towards-masochism/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Bashore|first1=Nicholas|title='Dark Souls 3' and the Problem with Regional Release Dates|url=https://www.inverse.com/article/14019-dark-souls-3-and-the-problem-with-regional-release-dates|website=inverse.com|accessdate=2016-04-09|archive-date=2016-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160416015801/https://www.inverse.com/article/14019-dark-souls-3-and-the-problem-with-regional-release-dates|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Leack|first1=Jonathan|title=Dark Souls 3's Launch Has Been Poorly Handled By Bandai Namco|url=http://www.gamerevolution.com/manifesto/dark-souls-3s-launch-has-been-poorly-handled-by-bandai-namco-36405|website=Game Revolution|accessdate=2016-04-05|archive-date=2016-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160403133713/http://www.gamerevolution.com/manifesto/dark-souls-3s-launch-has-been-poorly-handled-by-bandai-namco-36405|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[Polygon|Polygon]]》成員Philip Kollar為遊戲給予7/10分，對遊戲缺乏驚喜和隨意式的設計表示失望，認為不論在世界設計、節奏和技術層面，《黑暗靈魂III》均未達水準<ref name="Polygon"/>。在4月9日推出的修補檔案修正了部分評論員提及的畫面更新率與技術問題<ref>{{cite web|last1=Imtiaz|first1=Khurram|title=Dark Souls 3 Gets Patch 1.03 In Japan, Tweaks Gameplay And Improves Performance|url=http://gearnuke.com/dark-souls-3-gets-patch-1-03-japan-tweaks-gameplay-improves-performance/|website=GearNuke|accessdate=2016-05-26|archive-date=2016-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160410151649/http://gearnuke.com/dark-souls-3-gets-patch-1-03-japan-tweaks-gameplay-improves-performance/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 行銷 ==
遊戲發行兩星期後，PlayStation 4版本於日本售出超過二十萬份<ref>{{cite web|last1=Seeto|first1=Damian|title=Dark Souls 3 Sales Impress In Japan|url=http://attackofthefanboy.com/news/dark-souls-3-sales-impress-japan/|website=AttackoftheFanboy|publisher=Modern Media Group LLC|accessdate=2016-05-26|archive-date=2016-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160409045454/http://attackofthefanboy.com/news/dark-souls-3-sales-impress-japan/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。遊戲也成為萬代首天銷售情況最好與售出速度最快的作品<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/04/18/dark-souls-3-is-bandai-namcos-fastest-selling-game-ever|title=Dark Souls 3 Is Bandai Namco's Fastest Selling Game Ever|first=Matt|last=Potter|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2016-04-18|accessdate=2016-04-19|archive-date=2016-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160419203133/http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/04/18/dark-souls-3-is-bandai-namcos-fastest-selling-game-ever|dead-url=no}}</ref>。萬代於2016年5月10日宣佈遊戲已在全球發行超過三百萬份：五十萬份銷住日本和亞洲，一百五十萬份銷住北美，一百萬份銷往歐洲<ref>{{cite web|last1=Romano|first1=Sal|title=Dark Souls III tops three million shipments, Dark Souls series tops 13 million|url=http://gematsu.com/2016/05/dark-souls-iii-tops-three-million-shipments-dark-souls-series-tops-13-million|website=Gametsu|accessdate=2016-05-11|archive-date=2016-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160511090824/http://gematsu.com/2016/05/dark-souls-iii-tops-three-million-shipments-dark-souls-series-tops-13-million|dead-url=no}}</ref>。有報告指出此遊戲成為北美地區首天銷量最好的軟體<ref>{{cite web|last1=Grubb|first1=Jeff|title=April 2016 NPD: Dark Souls III, Ratchet & Clank lead as gaming industry drops 15%|url=http://venturebeat.com/2016/05/12/april-2016-npd-dark-souls-iii-ratchet-clank-lead-as-gaming-industry-drops-15/|website=Venturebeat|accessdate=2016-05-15|archive-date=2016-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160530191027/http://venturebeat.com/2016/05/12/april-2016-npd-dark-souls-iii-ratchet-clank-lead-as-gaming-industry-drops-15/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

